## 7. DMMFHelper - Convenience Wrapper

The `DMMFHelper` class (in `client-generator-ts/src/dmmf.ts`) provides convenient access patterns:

```typescript
export class DMMFHelper implements DMMF.Document {
  // Direct access to document
  document: DMMF.Document

  // Useful properties
  get datamodel(): DMMF.Datamodel
  get schema(): DMMF.Schema
